nexIRC 4

Link IRC and Matrix chat together

How to get started ...

Build the code, and run 'nexIRC4.exe'

You will be prompted to enter settings ...
- IRC Nickname
- IRC Alternative
- IRC Name
- IRC Channel
- IRC Server Name
- IRC Server Address
- IRC Port
- Matrix Node Address
- Matrix Username
- Matrix Password
- Matrix MachineID
- Matrix ChannelID

Click 'Connect' in the settings dialog.
In the client, type /matrix join <channelid> and hit enter (this joins the matrix channel)
After that, you are ready to use the matrix link with irc
